Package com.github.tommyettinger.gand.utils

Interface SearchProcessor<V>

Type Parameters:
V - the type parameter for each SearchStep; the vertex type
All Superinterfaces:
ObjectConsumer<SearchStep<V>>
public interface SearchProcessor<V> extends ObjectConsumer<SearchStep<V>>
Essentially the same as a Consumer<SearchStep<V>>, this is a functional interface that is typically run by search algorithms at each step. Its functional method is ObjectConsumer.accept(Object), where accept is given a SearchStep of type V.
